%% Status: NEEDS HUMAN REVIEW
sequenceDiagram
    participant Player
    participant AppLifecycle
    participant RecapService
    participant Supabase
    participant RecapScreen
    participant ObservabilityService

    Note over Player,AppLifecycle: App comes to foreground (or cold start after auth)
    AppLifecycle->>AppLifecycle: Check: last_recap_dismissed_at < now() - 6 hours?

    alt Less than 6 hours since last dismissal
        AppLifecycle->>AppLifecycle: Skip recap, go to active state
    else 6+ hours since last dismissal
        AppLifecycle->>RecapService: Request recap data

        RecapService->>Supabase: Query personal discoveries since last session
        Supabase-->>RecapService: Discovery data
        RecapService->>Supabase: Query progress stats (streaks, collection progress)
        Supabase-->>RecapService: Progress data
        RecapService->>Supabase: Query community aggregates (city, state, country)
        Supabase-->>RecapService: Community data
        RecapService->>Supabase: Query pending unidentified count
        Supabase-->>RecapService: Pending count

        Note over RecapService: No pre-computed cron for MVP.<br/>All queries run on-demand.

        RecapService->>RecapScreen: Build card stack: What's New, Your Progress, Community, Pending
        RecapScreen->>ObservabilityService: Log recap.shown

        RecapScreen->>Player: Show swipeable card stack

        Player->>RecapScreen: Swipe through cards or tap to skip

        RecapScreen->>Supabase: UPDATE last_recap_dismissed_at = now()
        RecapScreen->>ObservabilityService: Log recap.dismissed with pages_viewed count

        RecapScreen->>AppLifecycle: Navigate to active PackScreen
    end
